{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891320/extras/Chaos_Islands.gif?t=1732561450\" />City-building meets deck-building in Chaos Islands. Defend against demons, explore the skies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891320/extras/Settlement.png?t=1732561450\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Establish and expand your floating settlement in the skies, strategically placing structures to gather essential resources. Raise defenses to protect against demon attacks and ensure the survival of your community. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891320/extras/Settlement.gif?t=1732561450\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891320/extras/Defeat.png?t=1732561450\" />Defend your settlement with diverse strategies and card abilities to repel demon assaults and keep your settlement safe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891320/extras/Defeat_Constraction.gif?t=1732561450\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891320/extras/Assemble.png?t=1732561450\" />Customize your arsenal by collecting cards that represent various constructions and spells empowering you to adapt and overcome the challenges of the skies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891320/extras/Merchant.gif?t=1732561450\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891320/extras/Enemies.png?t=173256145